HEADWORD: Graspless
<hw>Grasp"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Without a grasp;
relaxed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>From my graspless hand Drop friendship's precious pearls.</q>
<rj><qau>Coleridge.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Grass</ent>⟦br⟧
